.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-PAY-COUNT-BY-DAY" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-pay-count-by-day \- FEAT-2276 count of complete pays grouped by calendar day
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-pay-count-by-day
.SH DESCRIPTION
node-pay-count-by-day for lightning CLI (FEAT-2276).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN. Returns a dictionary mapping UTC calendar days (YYYY-MM-DD) to the number of completed payments on that day.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
